<div id="review_2813793354" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2813793354" />
    <a title="Lost Planet Airman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3673987-lost-planet-airman"><img alt="Lost Planet Airman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1620012982p2/3673987.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2813793354?book_show_action=true">Oct 06, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lost Planet Airman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lost Planet Airman" href="/user/show/3673987-lost-planet-airman">Lost Planet Airman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3673987-lost-planet-airman?shelf=read-sf-award-supplementary">read-sf-award-supplementary</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3673987-lost-planet-airman?shelf=sffbc-tbr-19">sffbc-tbr-19</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3673987-lost-planet-airman?shelf=fos-redeemed">fos-redeemed</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2813793354" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8227412851249695415">Four tales of in the Hainish &apos;cycle&apos;, of the planets Werel and Yeowe and the end of racial slavery there.<br/><br/>These stories are more along the lines of <i>The Dispossessed</i>, more character driven and less plot driven, and they have taken me forever to get through (just because they never truly gripped me).<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText8227412851249695415" style="display:none">Four tales of in the Hainish 'cycle', of the planets Werel and Yeowe and the end of racial slavery there.<br /><br />These stories are more along the lines of <i>The Dispossessed</i>, more character driven and less plot driven, and they have taken me forever to get through (just because they never truly gripped me).<br /></span>
